06:02.359 --> 06:06.027
Mr. Thomas, I'm dr. Halstead.

06:06.096 --> 06:06.861
I heard you had
an incident at work today.

06:06.930 --> 06:11.633
Yeah, I guess I, fell down.

06:11.701 --> 06:15.103
The ems report says
they found you unconscious.

06:15.172 --> 06:17.939
How long you been
coughing up blood?

06:18.008 --> 06:21.242
