go rest up at home.

06:31.822 --> 06:36.458
Yeah, I don't blame ya,
but I fear if you go home,

06:36.527 --> 06:38.960
You may have a far worse event.

06:39.029 --> 06:39.394
Than whatever happened
this morning.

06:39.463 --> 06:42.264
That's okay.

06:42.332 --> 06:45.867
Well, you're too dehydrated
to walk out of here,

06:45.936 --> 06:46.468
