06:53.978 --> 06:54.978
All right.

06:59.216 --> 07:03.218
Syncope, weight loss,
hemoptysis.

07:03.287 --> 07:04.052
He's got cancer, right?

07:04.121 --> 07:05.131
A lot of people
are more afraid of.

07:05.155 --> 07:09.024
