and talk to him again.

07:23.074 --> 07:25.841
So, um, robert haywood is here.

07:25.910 --> 07:26.842
For a thoracic p.E.T. Scan?

07:26.911 --> 07:28.155
Yeah, we're doing
a full cardiac workup.

07:28.179 --> 07:31.513
You think you could add
a... a head study of that for me?

07:31.582 --> 07:34.083
