missing anything on my end.

07:34.151 --> 07:35.271
Sure, no problem. Thank you.

07:41.325 --> 07:42.158
Iaura...

07:42.226 --> 07:45.628
Your membranes
ruptured prematurely,

07:45.696 --> 07:46.707
Allowing an infection
in your uterus.

07:46.731 --> 07:49.532
