delivering this baby,

07:49.600 --> 07:50.099
The greater the danger
you're both in.

07:50.168 --> 07:53.069
So deliver it then.

07:53.137 --> 07:53.836
We need to do it
at the hospital.

07:53.905 --> 07:54.770
No, I told you, I'm not going.

07:54.839 --> 07:57.707
I understand that
you don't want to,

07:57.775 --> 07:58.541
But this is a safety issue,
okay?

07:58.610 --> 08:01.544
You need to think
about your baby.

08:01.613 --> 08:02.613
