to get him off.

09:16.221 --> 09:17.154
He could die.

09:17.222 --> 09:20.290
Then we make sure that
nothing goes wrong.

09:24.730 --> 09:25.162
Thank you.

09:25.230 --> 09:28.198
Mr. Thomas...

09:31.503 --> 09:35.172
We found a large growth
in your larynx.

09:35.241 --> 09:37.808
It's almost certainly cancer.

09:37.877 --> 09:41.879
All right.

09:41.947 --> 09:42.779
Now, the good news is,

09:42.848 --> 09:43.992
We have an excellent
oncology department,

09:44.016 --> 09:47.217
So I'd like to arrange for
a biopsy and a consultation,

09:47.286 --> 09:50.053
