It's okay.

09:50.122 --> 09:51.021
I'm not interested.

09:51.090 --> 09:53.691
Mr. Thomas, the sooner
you begin treatment,

09:53.759 --> 09:56.093
The better your chances
of survival.

09:56.162 --> 09:58.662
You don't understand. I'm...

09:58.731 --> 10:00.698
I'm ready to die.

10:04.637 --> 10:05.502
I know it's a lot
of information,

10:05.571 --> 10:08.272
And it can seem overwhelming,
but I...

10:08.341 --> 10:10.774
I said no.

10:14.480 --> 10:17.381
Can you tell me why you're
so resistant to treatment?

10:18.184 --> 10:22.353
Because I've made it 56 years.

10:22.422 --> 10:25.423
Without molesting a child,

10:25.491 --> 10:29.060
And I can't stand it anymore.

10:29.128 --> 10:30.128
I'm sorry?

10:32.365 --> 10:35.933
I'm a pedophile...

10:36.002 --> 10:38.269
And I wanna die.

10:45.770 --> 10:46.770
Yeah?

10:46.872 --> 10:50.440
Have you seen this yet?

