Can't you agree on what to do?

13:13.720 --> 13:15.987
It's not a black and white
situation.

13:19.326 --> 13:22.660
You've been treating him,
dr. Rhodes.

13:22.729 --> 13:23.729
What should we do?

13:27.401 --> 13:28.511
