13:28.535 --> 13:33.505
It's still our best chance
that he gets those lungs.

13:33.573 --> 13:34.172
Okay.

13:34.241 --> 13:38.610
Yes. That's what we'll do.

13:38.679 --> 13:39.679
All right.

13:44.952 --> 13:46.062
