his depression.

14:49.317 --> 14:50.394
You're not gonna do
the same for pedophilia?

14:50.418 --> 14:53.686
I just don't know that much
about pedophilia.

14:53.755 --> 14:56.555
Well, you better find out
fast, because he's dying.

14:56.624 --> 14:59.525
Department charge nurse
maggie lockwood,

14:59.594 --> 15:00.671
