insurance coverage.

15:10.672 --> 15:13.773
All right.
This driver, john gates,

15:13.842 --> 15:14.919
Do you know him?
Yeah, he's a jerk.

15:14.943 --> 15:18.911
Page me when he comes in.

15:18.980 --> 15:19.746
